  "texts": [
    "The ChID dataset serves as a platform for evaluating models in the context of Chinese idiomatic expression reading comprehension.",
    "In this task, models are tasked with filling in the blanks by choosing the appropriate idiom based on the provided context.",
    "The dataset specifically targets the models' comprehension of Chinese idioms and has been incorporated into the CLUE benchmark for assessing Chinese NLU capabilities.",
    "• CLOTH (Xie et al, 2018).",
    "The CLOTH dataset stands as the pioneer in clozetype reading comprehension datasets crafted manually."
  ],
